CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 2, 2011

[Cite as 02/02/2011 Case Announcements #2, 2011-Ohio-440.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2010-1894. Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Trainor.

This cause is before the court upon the filing by respondent of a motion to vacate the court’s order of January 24, 2011. Upon consideration thereof, the motion is denied.
